     <div type="dedication">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>The Authors Dedication.</head>
   <p>TO THEE O IESVS CHRIST, Son of the living God, and borne <hi>of the Virgin</hi> Mary, Lord of the living and of the dead, Doe I with <hi>Teares</hi> and <hi>Groanes,</hi> Give, Dedicate, and Consecrate These my CONTEMPLATIONS and SIGHES: And doe begge and beseech thee that thou wilt make them unto mee
<list>
         <item>A helpe in my life,</item>
         <item>A comfort at my death,</item>
         <item>My protection in Iudgement.</item>
      </list>
   </p>
   <closer>
      <signed>Thy adorer, redeemed by thy blood, J.M.D.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
